Use case: Update member records
Context: Edit a ChocAn member’s information, extends into adding, deleting, or editing
Actors: ChocAn Operator
Main Success Scenario: 
1. Receive information changes from operator
2. Update the corresponding information
Communicate to ACME to update member information if it is relevant to the monthly billing process
Extensions:
2a. Add member to directory
2b. Remove member from directory
2c. Edit member information

